				<section>
				<div align="left">
					Annual basis compensated with monthly payments: $$ y_t - \frac{1}{12+\lambda} \; G(12y_t)  $$ 

					Income Averaging (Vickrey 1939):
          $$ {g_{t}^{V}}= \frac{t}{T} G\left(T\frac{\sum_{p=0}^{t}y_{p}}{t}\right) -\sum_{p=0}^{t-1}g_{p}^{V}$$  
					<br>

					<b>Theoretical result:</b> The equal payement system is pareto improving compared to the anual basis scheme with the equal payment scheme.
						<aside class="notes">
